DataElement.preferredDefinition: A grouping of things based on shared common attributes.:Any number of entities (members) considered as a unit._A part of a thing, or of several things, taken to demonstrate or to determine the character of the whole, e.g. a substance, or portion of material obtained for use in testing, examination, or study; particularly, a preparation of tissue or bodily fluid taken for examination or diagnosis.:The words or language units by which a thing is known._Generic value domain for a java datatype that is a class that represents character strings.
